# L1-4: Double-sided dielectric slab — Snell + transmission power conservation
# Front face at x=2, back face at x=2.3 (0.3m thick wall)
# Validates: Snell's law, Fresnel transmission coefficients, power conservation
o slab_front
v 2.0 -50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 50.0 50.0
v 2.0 -50.0 50.0
vn -1.0 0.0 0.0
f 1//1 2//1 3//1
f 1//1 3//1 4//1

o slab_back
v 2.3 -50.0 -50.0
v 2.3 50.0 -50.0
v 2.3 50.0 50.0
v 2.3 -50.0 50.0
vn 1.0 0.0 0.0
f 5//2 7//2 6//2
f 6//2 7//2 8//2
